00:48:33,329 --> 00:48:35,320
זה אוסר עליו, harei zeh oser alav, they make it all forbidden

981
00:48:35,320 --> 00:48:38,020
to you. You can't make, according to the simple sense of this

982
00:48:38,020 --> 00:48:40,440
משנה, Mishna, you can't make an עירוב eruv, in the courtyard. You're

