00:49:03,300 --> 00:49:05,280
rights to your חלק, chelek, so you don't

991
00:49:06,340 --> 00:49:09,020
have, your membership or non-membership is irrelevant.

992
00:49:10,100 --> 00:49:13,660
Okay, but without renting, you cannot become part of the עירוב eruv?

993
00:49:13,660 --> 00:49:16,020
and therefore you create a problem. Let's keep on reading a little

994
00:49:16,020 --> 00:49:16,140
bit.

995
00:49:16,520 --> 00:49:17,229
It's not like he's there for...

